SELECT image_id, patient_id, image_data FROM imaging_data WHERE date_taken BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01' ORDER BY patient_id DESC, date_taken ASC;
SELECT patient_id, image_id, date_taken, COUNT(*) AS num_images FROM imaging_data GROUP BY patient_id ORDER BY num_images DESC;

SELECT images.image_id, images.image_date, diseases.disease_name FROM images JOIN detections ON images.image_id = detections.image_id JOIN diseases ON detections.disease_id = diseases.disease_id WHERE diseases.disease_name = 'Cancer' ORDER BY images.image_date DESC;

SELECT patients.patient_name, diseases.disease_name, detections.detection_date FROM patients JOIN detections ON patients.patient_id = detections.patient_id JOIN diseases ON detections.disease_id = diseases.disease_id WHERE detections.detection_result = TRUE ORDER BY detections.detection_date DESC;
